title: Danny & Lisa Ann Walter (ABC's Abbott Elementary/The Parent Trap)
itunes:title: Danny & Lisa Ann Walter (ABC's Abbott Elementary/The Parent Trap)
description:
Danny chats with comedian Lisa Ann Walter, who most know as Chessy from The Parent Trap, she now is one of the stars of Abbott Elementary on ABC, which is one of the best shows on TV! Lisa and Danny talk about working on the 1996 Whoopi Goldberg film, Eddie, War of the Worlds with Tom Cruise, Shall We Dance with Richard Gere and JLO, and so much more!


TOUR TICKETS: https://everythingiconic.com/live-shows
